CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "Grads Of The College, Soldiers, Teachers - ...center photo: D. Herbert Wallace and Robert McCoy Higginbotham were commissioned second lieutenants in Air Corps Reserve. Wallace was designated as one of eleven "Distinguished Military" graduates..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Air Corps Reserve second lieutenants and University of Pittsburgh graduates D. Herbert Wallace and Robert McCoy Higginbotham, posed on lawn in front of Syria Mosque, Oakland
